Whats Interesting about the Uinibroues is that the color of the label represents the flavor. Maudite tastes very "red" as Troid Pistoles tastes very "purple."


Its good for getting a buzz on, and if you want to drink beer with the devil on it. Thats gotta stand for something.
The stout from which all others are compared. The biggest problem with Guinness is how full it makes you, its a meal replacement in a bottle.
